event BuyOrder(address indexed token, uint256 id, bytes32 indexed hash, address seller, address indexed taker, uint256 price)
event CancelOrder(address indexed token, uint256 id, bytes32 indexed hash, address indexed seller)
event MakeOrder(address indexed token, uint256 id, bytes32 indexed hash, address indexed seller)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)

function bulkViewCollectionOrders(address _token, uint256 _fromIndex, uint16 _limit) view returns (tuple(address seller, address token, uint256 tokenId, uint256 listPrice, uint256 endBlock, bool isSold, bool isCancelled)[])

function bulkViewSellerOrders(address _seller, uint256 _fromIndex, uint16 _limit) view returns (tuple(address seller, address token, uint256 tokenId, uint256 listPrice, uint256 endBlock, bool isSold, bool isCancelled)[])
function onERC721Received(address, address, uint256, bytes) returns (bytes4)
function orderInfo(bytes32) view returns (address seller, address token, uint256 tokenId, uint256 listPrice, uint256 endBlock, bool isSold, bool isCancelled)
